# Results

This folder contains output from `scripts/stata/analysis.do`.

## File naming convention

| Suffix | Contents |
|---|---|
| `*_Beta.jpg` | Cohort-specific ATET coefficients (β̂_k) plotted by year |
| `*_SE.jpg` | Cohort-specific standard errors plotted by year |
| `*.jpg` | Event-study ATET plots from `estat atetplot` |
| `*.gph` | Stata graph files (editable) |
| `*.csv` | Raw regression output tables exported via `esttab` |

## Indicators covered

Imports, Exports, Gross Capital Formation, GDP Growth, Inflation, Unemployment, Current Account Balance, Exchange Rate (USD), Government Consumption

## Heterogeneity checks

Cross-indicator robustness plots (e.g. Exports → Imports, Government Consumption → GDP Growth) are also included.
